<br>
So wondering if anyone know's what's good to fight if your solo, I know what to go after with a group (mermaids, seahorses, sharks if any are close by, swirlspines are also good if Phinny's down).<br>
<br>
Things I like about this zone:<br>
- XP is great<br>
<br>
- Dungeon is usually vacant except possibly for a tracker watching for Phinny/Undertow. Sometimes a group might be there trying to get the tainted seahorse.<br>
<br>
- Cash is decent, mobs all drop plat, various gems (star rubies, sapphires, fire emeralds, etc).<br>
<br>
- Moving around this dungeon is a breeze once you know the routes. Only the named mobs can see through invis, and they can be avoided if you don't want to kill them. This makes it easy to come and go where as places like Seb or The Hole you need a group to move in, and an evac'er to get out (well, not the only way, certainly the most expediant).<br>
<br>
Great place to take a group, I'm just wondering what might be doable till I can get a group assembled. The other benefit of course, if your still working on your epic, watching for Undertow and Phinny is easier, and much more tolerable.<br>
<br>
