ing them out one by one and having to deal with their CHs in turn.  Swirlspines, in particular, are highly MR, can't be mezzed, have more hp than Seeking Flame could take out, and only a very small percentage of them can be hit by stun based spells.  They must be pushed to interrupt, or you need a professional stunner, which Mages and Mage's pets are not.<br>
